title: Fixed collision with earth and incoming meteorites.
message:
Fixed collision with earth and incoming meteorites.

Since LibGDX's ShapeRenderer renders circles in the center of the given coordinates (unlike the top-corner in Java's Graphics2D), the collision wasn't fully correct. I just adjusted the coordinates by substracting the radius of the x and y coordinate, so it now renders it from the left top corner.
